@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : listActiveRoutesSorted(sortBy)
activate System

note right of System: The system retrieves all active routes\nand sorts them by popularity (number of times used)\nor by distance, depending on the sortBy parameter.

System --> ATCC : returns sorted list of active routes with usage statistics
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
